com.ibm.team.scm.common.dto

Interface IWorkspaceSearchCriteria

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.ibm.team.scm.common.internal.IDateRangeSearchCriteria, com.ibm.team.scm.common.dto.IItemSearchCriteria, com.ibm.team.scm.common.internal.INamedSearchCritieria, IOrderedSearchCriteria, ISearchCriteria

    public interface IWorkspaceSearchCriteria
extends IOrderedSearchCriteria, com.ibm.team.scm.common.internal.INamedSearchCritieria, com.ibm.team.scm.common.internal.IDateRangeSearchCriteria
    This interface defines the criteria that workspaces can match. Every criteria can either be set or unset (set to null). When multiple criteria are set the result is the conjunction of all the criteria.
    Since:
    0.7

      • setRequireNameFilterUnion

        IWorkspaceSearchCriteria setRequireNameFilterUnion(boolean value)
        If true, find workspaces where the workspace name OR the owner name match. Otherwise, find workspaces where the workspace name AND the owner name match.
